OL,3,C'I am frankly stunned': Meloni rebukes
OL,4,CTrump claim she begged for selfie at G7
OL,6,FItaly's Prime Minister Giorgia Meloni
OL,7,Fhas hit back at Donald Trump's claim
OL,8,Fshe "begged" him for a selfie, as the
OL,9,Fnation's foreign minister abruptly
OL,10,Fcancelled a trip to the United States.
OL,12,FTrump made the comment during an
OL,13,Finterview with Italian broadcaster La7
OL,14,Fon Friday morning, after the leaders
OL,15,Fspent time together at the recent G7
OL,16,Fsummit in Evian-les-Bains, France.
OL,18,FThe interviewer had asked Trump about
OL,19,FUkraine, but the US president raised
OL,20,FMeloni instead, and the conversation
OL,21,Fturned to their earlier meeting.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
