OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1781982673
OL,3,C'I am frankly stunned': Meloni rebukes
OL,4,CTrump claim she begged for selfie at G7
OL,6,FAccording to La7, Trump said Meloni
OL,7,Fhad "begged" him for a photo-op. Trump
OL,8,Fsaid he wasn't obliged to do it, but
OL,9,Fthat he felt sorry for her and agreed,
OL,10,FLa7 said.
OL,12,FIn response, Italian Foreign Minister
OL,13,FAntonio Tajani abruptly cancelled a
OL,14,Fplanned trip to the United States this
OL,15,Fweekend, calling Trump's claims
OL,16,F"serious and offensive" toward Meloni
OL,17,Fand all of Italy.
OL,19,FAfter Trump made the claim, Meloni
OL,20,Fposted a video on social media
OL,21,Frebuking the US president.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
