OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1781982673
OL,3,C'I am frankly stunned': Meloni rebukes
OL,4,CTrump claim she begged for selfie at G7
OL,6,FSpeaking in Italian, Giorgia Meloni
OL,7,Frebuked Trump in a post on X
OL,9,FSpeaking in Italian, she said she was
OL,10,Fresponding to Trump's claims because
OL,11,F"certain things deserve an immediate
OL,12,Fresponse".
OL,14,F"Donald Trump's statements are
OL,15,Fcompletely fabricated. I am frankly
OL,16,Fstunned," she said. "I don't know why
OL,17,Fthe president of the United States
OL,18,Fbehaves this way toward his own
OL,19,Fallies. After all, this isn't the
OL,20,Ffirst time this has happened."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
