OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1781982673
OL,3,C'I am frankly stunned': Meloni rebukes
OL,4,CTrump claim she begged for selfie at G7
OL,6,FIt was an apparent reference to an
OL,7,Finterview Trump gave to Italian daily
OL,8,FCorriere della Sera in April, in which
OL,9,Fhe criticised Meloni's refusal to back
OL,10,Fthe US-Israel war in Iran. Meloni
OL,11,Fdidn't respond publicly at the time.
OL,13,FBy Friday, it appeared she had had
OL,14,Fenough of his boasts and broadsides.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
