OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1781982673
OL,3,C'I am frankly stunned': Meloni rebukes
OL,4,CTrump claim she begged for selfie at G7
OL,6,F"I can only say that it's a shame he
OL,7,Fdoesn't show the same resolve toward
OL,8,Fthe enemies of the West, toward the
OL,9,Fenemies of the United States, toward
OL,10,Fleaders with whom he, on the other
OL,11,Fhand, is much more accommodating,"
OL,12,FMeloni said.
OL,14,FShe added: "But there's one thing he
OL,15,Fmust remember: Italy and I do not beg."
