OL,3,C'I am frankly stunned': Meloni rebukes
OL,4,CTrump claim she begged for selfie at G7
OL,6,FMeloni had initially sought to build
OL,7,Fon longstanding strong US-Italian ties
OL,8,Fwhen Trump began his second term, and
OL,9,Fhad positioned herself as a "bridge"
OL,10,Fbetween Washington and the European
OL,11,FUnion. She was the lone EU head of
OL,12,Fstate to attend his inauguration.
OL,14,FBut relations have frayed over the US
OL,15,Fwar in Iran, which Meloni has called
OL,16,F"illegal", and Trump's position on
OL,17,FUkraine, which Italy strongly
OL,18,Fsupports. Trump's tariffs and strong
OL,19,FUS support of Israel over its war in
OL,20,FGaza have been other points of
OL,21,Fcontention.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
