OL,3,C'I am frankly stunned': Meloni rebukes
OL,4,CTrump claim she begged for selfie at G7
OL,6,FBy Friday afternoon, solidarity with
OL,7,FMeloni had poured in from across the
OL,8,Fgovernment and political spectrum, and
OL,9,Fincluded a call from President Sergio
OL,10,FMattarella, Italy's widely respected
OL,11,Fhead of state.
OL,13,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,14,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,15,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,16,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,18,F"Whoever attacks @GiorgiaMeloni
OL,19,Fattacks all of us," posted Transport
OL,20,FMinister Matteo Salvini.
OL,26,@zD@AOU{D@SO]
