OL,3,C'I am frankly stunned': Meloni rebukes
OL,4,CTrump claim she begged for selfie at G7
OL,6,FDefence Minister Guido Crosetto said
OL,7,Fhe didn't believe Meloni would ever
OL,8,Fbeg someone for a photo, "not even
OL,9,Funder threat."
OL,11,F"I can, however, imagine how much it
OL,12,Fcost her to set aside what Trump had
OL,13,Fsaid weeks ago, to serve the interests
OL,14,Fof Italy, of Europe, and of the West,"
OL,15,FCrosetto posted on X. "Jokes of this
OL,16,Fkind do no good to anyone: neither to
OL,17,Fthe USA, nor to Italy, nor to the
OL,18,Falliance."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/9
