OL,3,C'I am frankly stunned': Meloni rebukes
OL,4,CTrump claim she begged for selfie at G7
OL,6,FTajani had been due to travel to the
OL,7,FUS as early as Sunday to take part in
OL,8,Fan Italy-US business forum in Miami
OL,9,Fduring which he would have met with US
OL,10,FSecretary of State Marco Rubio,
OL,11,Faccording to the US State Department.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/9
